<h1>You what the hey now?</h1>
<p>OurSignal.com looks at currently popular items on RSS feeds and mashes them all together.</p>
<p>The idea is to allow users (you especially) to get a rapid overview of what the latest breaking headlines are at the frontline of the intermatubes.</p>
<p>Sources are refreshed every 20 minutes.</p>
